  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">NIAF 2 - Nigeria Infrastructure Advisory Facility Phase 2</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To enhance the management of Nigeria&#x2019;s infrastructure development towards power sector reform, capital spending, repair and maintenance of roads, climate change adaptation and mitigation. This is expected to result to increased economic growth, job creation and contribute towards the MDGs by significantly reducing poverty for the majority of the Nigeria populace by year 2020.</narrative>
  </description>
